entry.title: mineek/dirtycowapp
entry.summary:
DirtyCowApp

This is a all-in-one app for tweaks for iOS 16.1.2 and lower. It uses the MacDirtyCow exploit to overwrite files on the filesystem.

Credits

  • haxi0 for help with some tweaks ( No folder blur )
  • verygenericname for help with some tweaks ( Hide the dock )
